Lady Hawk searched the medical files from any past injuries the alliance
members might have had. she was hoping to simulate the DNA through the CR
chambers.





Phobias babies watched the happenings around KitKats group. they watched the
conference with Magnus and Gabriel with simulated interest. This was the
type of agreement Phobia was hoping for. Only through peace talks could the
temporal anomalies stop. either talks or destruction.


Veratis watched as the protoform took the shape of the DNA, then change into
owl form then a sort of robot form. he hadn't heard her in a while so either
the body was using to much energy or she'd learn to control it. He waited
anxiously for her to complete her transformation. He wanted to see what
other abilities she'd contracted.
